Posted Oct. 22, 2015 at 6:00 AM By TV Guide Posted Oct. 22, 2015 at 6:00 AM The Vikings are conquering Hulu! The show's third season will debut on the streaming service in November, along with a lot of James Bond films, early yuletide fare, Season 1 of Steven Universe and a fresh library of movies courtesy of the services' Showtime subscription add-on. Here's a complete list of Hulu's new arrivals, with Showtime-exclusive titles indicated. Available Nov. 1
